{"questionId": "dbe9b217", "correctAnswer": "68", "section": "Math", "steps": [{"title": "Substitute the value x = 2", "content": "Replace $x$ with $2$ in $$f(x) = 8x^3 + 4.$$ This gives $$f(2) = 8(2)^3 + 4.$$"}, {"title": "Compute the result", "content": "Simplify: $$f(2) = 8(8) + 4 = 64 + 4 = 68.$$ The answer is <strong>68</strong>.", "desmosExpressions": ["f(x)=8(x)^(3)+4"]}]}